data.title: Welcome to La Grange, TX
data.text:
La Grange will celebrate its 28th anniversary as a Main Street City in 2024!

We’re rich in Historic Assets, Old World Charm, and Downtown Shopping! We hope you’ll take a look around at everything our town has to offer, and then stop by and see us in person.

Don’t forget to check out the La Grange Daytripper episode. And if you’re planning ahead for summertime fun, be sure to take a look at the fun events we have in store. See you soon!
